title: Case Logic VNB-217 Value 17-Inch Laptop Backpack (Black)
description: Here’s proof that a backpack can be as polished and professional as a briefcase, the contemporary styling and smartly placed features of this streamlined backpack add up to perfect organization for your small electronics and protection for your 17-Inch laptop. Features: Dedicated compartment holds up to 17-Inch widescreen laptops; Organization panel stores your electronics, pens and more; External zippered Speed Pocket provides a secure place for quick access for your cell phone, Blackberry, etc; Expansive interior storage holds books, files and folders; External mesh pocket stores a water bottle, snacks and other miscellaneous items; 25 year warranty. Fits Up to 17.3-Inch laptops External Dimensions 18 x 12 x 18.5-Inch Laptop Compartment 16.4 x 12.2 x 1.8-Inch
